      diagnostics ‚Ü© AddIf ‚ü®diagnostics, prefixCount‚Č•‚Č†parsedCandidate.transactions, "suffix_transaction_missing", 0, "suffix must add at least one native transaction"‚ü©
      {ūĚēä:
