        suffixIds ‚Üź {<ūĚē©.source_event_id}¬®suffixTransactions
        overlap ‚Üź ‚ą®¬ī0‚ąĺ{IsOneOf ‚ü®>ūĚē©,prefixIds‚ü©}¬®suffixIds
        diagnostics ‚Ü© AddIf ‚ü®diagnostics, overlap, "suffix_transaction_duplicate", 0, "suffix transaction identity must not already occur in the prefix"‚ü©
      }‚ćü(prefixCount<‚Č†parsedCandidate.transactions) @
      {ūĚēä:
        stageA ‚Üź stage2a.Build ‚ü®parsedCandidate.transactions,resolved,cycleStart‚ü©
