          diagnostics ‚ąĺ‚Ü© stageB.diagnostics
          {ūĚēä: transactions‚Ü©parsedCandidate.transactions ‚čĄ postingRows‚Ü©stageA.posting_rows}‚ćü(stageB.state‚Č°"ok") @
        }‚ćü(stageA.state‚Č°"ok") @
