    }‚ćü((parsedPrefix.state‚Č°"ok") ‚ąß (parsedCandidate.state‚Č°"ok")) @
  }‚ćü(verified ‚ąß 0<‚Č†suffixBytes) @
  failed ‚Üź 0<‚Č†diagnostics
  transactionCount ‚Üź failed‚äĎ(‚Č†transactions)‚ÄŅ0
  postingCount ‚Üź failed‚äĎ(‚Č†postingRows)‚ÄŅ0
  outputTransactions ‚Üź failed‚äĎtransactions‚ÄŅempty
